Run the TCPS GUI to read, visualize and report on the data

Visualize the likert scale items comprising a lever

Read the TCPS from a qualtrics export file or files, and transform the data into a tidy format

Generate the boilerplate report from provided TCPS data

tcps_sample()

Retrieve file paths to TCPS sample data.

tcps_structure

A tibble containing the structure of each TCPS survey.

Calculate basic summary statistics for a tidied data frame of TCPS data

Read the TCPS from a qualtrics export file and transform the data into a tidy format
